{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d045cf98e0","title":"关于部队支左的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"40b3962d6b","index":0,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":null,"articleId":"d045cf98e0","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"谢富治","id":"93cca4665d","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961-1968卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"91d8b3f7fe","type":"title","text":"关于部队支左的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"d045cf98e0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"039d21a249","type":"paragraph","text":"军队的威信必须坚决维护，不能有半点含糊。拥军爱民社论的发表是当前工作的中心。军队第一次支左、支工、支农、军训、军管是大规模的战斗任务，犯错误是难免的，问题在于当前主要危险是有人把解放军打下去。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"d045cf98e0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1cec96222a","type":"paragraph","text":"支左支错，支到保守派方向去，改过来就行了，允许的嘛。我们在这五大工作中，三分之二做对了，三分之一做错了，就是很好了。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"d045cf98e0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ab21dc369c","type":"paragraph","text":"有的受老婆孩子观点的影响，有的是县委书记或地委书记，他们的孩子是那个地方的保守派，或者是老婆是那个地方当权派之一，这是值得我们警惕的。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"d045cf98e0","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":426,"end":426}},"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0bae75c7a2","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"d045cf98e0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0d854e8d36","type":"title","text":"关于部队支左的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"d045cf98e0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"156e4475a1","type":"paragraph","text":"军队的威信必须坚决维护，不能有半点含糊。拥军爱民社论的发表是当前工作的中心。军队第一次支左、支工、支农、军训、军管是大规模的战斗任务，犯错误是难免的，问题在于当前主要危险是有人把解放军打下去。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"d045cf98e0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"263064fbd9","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"d045cf98e0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4e7dba1713","type":"paragraph","text":"有的受老婆孩子观点的影响，有的是县委地委或地委书记，他们的孩子是那个地方的保守派，或者是老婆是那个地方当权派之一，这是值得我们警惕的。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"d045cf98e0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"687ff2c2d8","type":"paragraph","text":"支左支错，支到保守派方向去，改过来就行了，允许的嘛。我们在这五大工作中，三分之二做对了，三分之一做错了，就是很好了。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"d045cf98e0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"be539a3120","type":"paragraph","text":"（摘自谢富治付总理四月六日讲话）","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"d045cf98e0","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":575,"end":575}}}},"__N_SSG":true}